  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bowling Simulator is a realistic bowling game where you’ll feel like a pro landing strikes, thanks to its easy to use controls. Grab your favorite drink and hit the lanes at Nashville Bowling Center, where bowling isn’t just a game—it’s life!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/32cf66cd4c4e6d3c3207ce7e63b897c7.avif?t=1772361720\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/4ade6bef35b1ad948a7542aeac28cd7a.poster.avif?t=1772361720\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/4ade6bef35b1ad948a7542aeac28cd7a.webm?t=1772361720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/4ade6bef35b1ad948a7542aeac28cd7a.mp4?t=1772361720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Bowling Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bowling Simulator offers a realistic bowling experience with easy-to-master controls, letting you feel like a pro as you land perfect strikes. Whether you're playing casually or aiming for a perfect game, the gameplay ensures fun for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/0c495d3f54e99495dac2d2630f2a52e9.poster.avif?t=1772361720\" width=602 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/0c495d3f54e99495dac2d2630f2a52e9.webm?t=1772361720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/0c495d3f54e99495dac2d2630f2a52e9.mp4?t=1772361720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your favorite drink and take on 10 exciting rounds in single-player or local multiplayer at the lively Nashville Bowling Center. Here, bowling is more than just a game—it’s a way of life!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bowling Simulator is a realistic bowling game where you’ll feel like a pro landing strikes, thanks to its easy to use controls. Grab your favorite drink and hit the lanes at Nashville Bowling Center, where bowling isn’t just a game—it’s life!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/32cf66cd4c4e6d3c3207ce7e63b897c7.avif?t=1772361720\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/4ade6bef35b1ad948a7542aeac28cd7a.poster.avif?t=1772361720\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/4ade6bef35b1ad948a7542aeac28cd7a.webm?t=1772361720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/4ade6bef35b1ad948a7542aeac28cd7a.mp4?t=1772361720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Bowling Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bowling Simulator offers a realistic bowling experience with easy-to-master controls, letting you feel like a pro as you land perfect strikes. Whether you're playing casually or aiming for a perfect game, the gameplay ensures fun for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990/extras/0c495d3f54e99495dac2d2630f2a52e9.poster.avif?t=1772361720\" width=602 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405990